title: S17 Ep51: Exploring Strange and Scary Stories with Jim Harold
itunes:title: Exploring Strange and Scary Stories with Jim Harold
description:
Darkness Radio presents Exploring Strange and Scary Stories with Jim Harold!

Today on the show, we welcome back old friend and Podcaster, Jim Harold!  We catch up with Jim on what is going on with his shows, The Paranormal Podcast and Jim Harold's Campfire. talk about the strange happenings in our time, and manage to get some of those strange and spooky stories that Jim is so famous for!

 Check out Jim's shows wherever you download your podcasts, or get your premium subscriptions here: https://jimharold.com/

Darkness Radio has partnered with the UFO Disclosure Symposium in late May! Be part of this newsworthy conference and get your tickets here: https://ufodisclosuresymposium.com/?ref=tim%40darknessradio.com
